The Alex Jones Show
Monday, 16 September 2013


[sebaygo1]


Show Description
................

From the Infowars web site :: On this Monday, September 16 edition of The Alex Jones Show, Alex covers the Navy Yard shooting in Washington D.C. as gun control legislation remains stalled in Congress and the political agenda of the gun grabbers is in sore need of a propaganda infusion to get off dead center. 

Terry Holcomb of Open Carry and Rachel Malone of Texas Firearms Freedom are in-studio to talk with Alex about the unfolding event in Washington and Holcomb's arrest of over the weekend for carrying a legal firearm during an Open Carry demonstration at the Texas capitol in Austin. 

Alex also talks with film, television, stage, and voice actor and former president of the Screen Actors Guild, Ed Asner on today's worldwide broadcast. Asner further critiques Obama's remarks that those who criticize his policies are racist.
